## anon-connection-wizard (started by setup-wizard-dist) edits Tor config
## files, therefore needs root.
## For better usability, because otherwise the autostart of setup-wizard-dist
## at first boot would require password entry.
## Feel free to disable it.
## Legacy.
%sudo ALL=NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/setup-wizard-dist setup
## New.
%sudo ALL=NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/setup-wizard-dist
